&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Seyond&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Seyond is a global provider of image‑grade LiDAR technology, enabling high‑precision 3D perception for automotive, intelligent transportation, robotics, and industrial automation applications. Founded in Silicon Valley in 2016, Seyond builds technologies that bridge the digital and physical worlds—making mobility and infrastructure safer, smarter, and more autonomous.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In 2025, Seyond shipped&amp;nbsp;over 332,000 LiDAR units worldwide, achieving&amp;nbsp;45% year‑on‑year growth. With a&amp;nbsp;positive gross margin the company has entered a new phase of sustainable, high‑quality growth, driven by scale, operational excellence, and a strong product portfolio.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Seyond operates a&amp;nbsp;global footprint, with R&amp;amp;D centers in Silicon Valley and Suzhou and manufacturing facilities in the United States and China. The company is a pioneer in the mass production of both&amp;nbsp;1550 nm and 905 nm LiDAR technologies, supporting deployment in real‑world, high‑volume applications across multiple industries.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Seyond, you’ll work with international teams at the forefront of perception technology, helping bring advanced LiDAR solutions from development into large‑scale production and customer deployment. We offer an environment that values technical excellence, collaboration, and real‑world impact—shaping how machines see and understand the world around them.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Seyond Europe&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Seyond Europe GmbH is the sole subsidiary of the Seyond Group in Europe. Based in Eschborn, Germany, Seyond Europe is responsible for business development, technical support, and logistics across Europe, India, Africa, and the United Arab Emirates. We work closely with customers and partners to deploy advanced LiDAR solutions any kind of applications.&lt;/p&gt;
